stories.title: Sri Lanka v Bangladesh
stories.subTitle: First one-day international
stories.summary: At Sinhalese Sports Club, Colombo, August 4

stories.title: Sri Lanka in full swing at SSC
stories.summary:
With three `papara' bands in full swing under the corrugated tin roofs at
the Sinhalese Sports Club, Sri Lanka celebrated the return of Aravinda de
Silva and Muttiah Muralitharan to their one-day side, cruising to a
comfortable five-wicket win
